# User Stories

## Business Users
- **As a Sales Manager**, I want to view monthly revenue by country so I can compare performance across regions.
- **As a Marketing Head**, I want to track product categories with high churn risk so I can launch recovery campaigns.
- **As a CEO**, I want a high-level dashboard with total revenue and churn KPIs so I can make quick strategic decisions.

## Technical Users
- **As a Data Engineer**, I want to automate ETL from CSV to Redshift so data is available for reporting.
- **As a BI Analyst**, I want to build Tableau visuals for churn and KPIs to support business insights.
